OL,3,CMayor blasts rail operators for
OL,4,Cweather 'chaos'
OL,6,FA metro mayor has slammed rail
OL,7,Foperators for the "unnecessary chaos"
OL,8,Fon services after severe weather hit
OL,9,Fthe region.
OL,11,FSteve Rotheram, Liverpool City Region
OL,12,FMayor, said he shared the anger of
OL,13,FMerseyrail users following widespread
OL,14,Fdisruption to services across the
OL,15,Fnetwork, with delays and cancellations
OL,16,Fas the frost and ice took hold.
OL,18,FIt comes just months after
OL,19,Fshareholders received #42 million in
OL,20,Fdividends.
