OL,3,CMayor blasts rail operators for
OL,4,Cweather 'chaos'
OL,6,FIn a video posted on social media Mr
OL,7,FRotheram announced that there would be
OL,8,Fan independent review into the
OL,9,Fproblems.
OL,11,FHe said: "While the poor weather
OL,12,Fconditions have caused problems to
OL,13,Fpublic transport all over the country,
OL,14,Fmy concern is what happens in
OL,15,FLiverpool city region. As a country we
OL,16,Fdon't do 'bad weather' well.
OL,26,@sD@JOU
