OL,3,CMayor blasts rail operators for
OL,4,Cweather 'chaos'
OL,6,F"This morning's severe disruption to
OL,7,FMerseyrail services due to cold
OL,8,Fweather is completely unacceptable.
OL,9,FIt's not as if there were six-foot
OL,10,Fsnow drifts.
OL,12,F"For thousands of people across our
OL,13,Fregion ` myself included ` it's meant
OL,14,Fdelays getting to work, missed
OL,15,Fhospital appointments, and unnecessary
OL,16,Fchaos.
OL,18,F"As someone who regularly uses our
OL,19,Fpublic transport system to get around,
OL,20,FI've seen first-hand the frustration
OL,21,Fthat this kind of failure causes.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
