OL,3,CMayor blasts rail operators for
OL,4,Cweather 'chaos'
OL,6,F"The fragmentation of the rail network
OL,7,Foften results in confusion around who
OL,8,Fis responsible for what bit of the
OL,9,Fsystem," he said.
OL,11,F"That's why today I have commissioned
OL,12,Fan independent and rapid review into
OL,13,Fthis week's disruption on the
OL,14,FMerseyrail network.
OL,16,F"Let me be clear: this isn't just
OL,17,Fabout trains not running. It's about
OL,18,Fthe real-world impact on people's
OL,19,Flives ` the stress, the missed
OL,20,Fopportunities, and the disruption it
OL,21,Fcauses.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@HO]sD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
