OL,3,CMayor blasts rail operators for
OL,4,Cweather 'chaos'
OL,6,F"And while freezing conditions might
OL,7,Fcause challenges, there's no excuse
OL,8,Ffor other aspects such as the poor
OL,9,Fcommunication passengers have
OL,10,Fexperienced. They deserve clear,
OL,11,Ftimely information, not to be left in
OL,12,Fthe dark."
OL,14,FMr Rotheram is keen to take greater
OL,15,Fcontrol of the network once the
OL,16,Fcurrent franchise ends in 2028.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@JO]
