OL,6,FThe findings of the review will be
OL,7,Freported at next month's Combined
OL,8,FAuthority meeting, in addition to
OL,9,Fwhich representatives from Network
OL,10,FRail, Merseyrail and train
OL,11,Fmanufacturer Stadler will be asked to
OL,12,Fattend the next meeting of the
OL,13,FCombined Authority's Transport
OL,14,FCommittee on 30 January.
